****EVEREST BASE CAMP****
*****October 2nd  2023***** 

My soul is full, my heart is happy, Everest you are majestic and magnificent, a beauty I have never seen or experienced before, Thank you for allowing me to safely visit you, for expanding my mind and my heart on a journey I don’t think words will ever describe, What I have seen with my own eyes will be emblazoned in my mind and heart forever, the beautiful Sherpa people I have been blessed to meet and spend time with, their kindness, their grit, their faith, they are people with the biggest hearts, this journey has forever changed me in the best way possible, it has expanded my mind, my heart, and pushed my body to an extreme, but every single step was worth it to be in the presence of the ever beautiful Everest! 
And finally - Thank you to my incredible husband who took on dad duties for the three weeks I have been away to allow me to go on this adventure, I will eternally be grateful-  I’m coming home a better person for it- I love you @paulcasey_golf. 

**** THE WORLD IS A BOOK- AND THOSE WHO DO NOT TRAVEL READ ONLY ONE PAGE- Saint Augustine*****
